OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782497915
OL,3,CMan arrested after homes evacuated in
OL,4,CHemlington
OL,6,FA man has been arrested after a
OL,7,F"standoff" with police forced the
OL,8,Fevacuation of more than 20 homes on a
OL,9,FMiddlesbrough street.
OL,11,FOfficers were called to a property on
OL,12,FOsbourne Close, near Hemlington Lake
OL,13,Fat around 7:30am on Thursday (25 June).
OL,15,FSpecialist teams attended and a cordon
OL,16,Fwas put in place, with nearby
OL,17,Fresidents evacuated.
OL,19,FA 48-year-old man has now been
OL,20,Farrested following the incident.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
