OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782497915
OL,3,CMan arrested after homes evacuated in
OL,4,CHemlington
OL,6,FDetective Chief Superintendent
OL,7,FCaroline McGlade from Cleveland Police
OL,8,Fsaid: "Following a significant
OL,9,Fstandoff on Osbourne Close, we have
OL,10,Farrested a 48-year-old man for
OL,11,Fnumerous offences.
OL,13,F"The cordon will remain in place
OL,14,Fwhilst searches of the property
OL,15,Fcontinue and the flat is secured. As
OL,16,Fsoon as it is safe for residents to
OL,17,Freturn home, we will communicate this
OL,18,Falongside our partners.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1782497915
OL,3,CMan arrested after homes evacuated in
OL,4,CHemlington
OL,6,F"I would like to thank residents who
OL,7,Fhave been displaced for their patience
OL,8,Fand cooperation.
OL,10,F"I would also like to thank Cleveland
OL,11,FPolice officers, our partners, and
OL,12,Fspecialist support from other forces
OL,13,Ffor their assistance today. It has
OL,14,Fbeen a challenging operation in
OL,15,Fadverse weather conditions. They have
OL,16,Fcollectively shown a commitment to the
OL,17,Fprotection of the community and
OL,18,Fbrought the events to a safe
OL,19,Fconclusion."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/3
